   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Educate a Deaf Child, Create a Future - Mexico</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Escuela de Educacion Especial de San Miguel de Allende provides free education and vocational training to those who are Deaf, at all levels and for all ages. A bi-lingual model of Mexican Sign Language and written Spanish ensure that the students can thrive in an inclusive environment where they learn and progress within a community of their peers.  Due to Covid-19 the school has pivoted to on-line virtual learning, opening up a broader landscape of opportunities, some newly discovered.</narrative>
  </description>
